versions.description: So many goodies. Rewrite for Get-CognosReport, Save-CognosReport. Pipe Reports to Get-CognosReport and Get-CognosDataSet.
Added Get-CogSqlData and Update-CogTableDefintions. Use Write-Progress for waiting on Report.
Added RefID to Start-CognosReport to reference a ConversationID. Added Get-CognosDataSet.
Fix for Save-CognosReport timeout on larger reports.
File format fix, Save-CognosReport and Get-CognosReport now use Start-CognosReport.
